products.name: Belgin 13
products.description: Belgin Ultra 13, a new Belgian gin, distilled according to old principles. The Belgin Ultra 13 has an own personality, a very nice gin with a complicated taste.

products.name: Tanqueray Nr10
products.description: Just like the Tanqueray Special Dry, the Nr10 has an alcohol percentage of about 47,30 %. This gin as introduced for the first time in 2000 and is a nice addition to the portfolio of this producer.
